agentData.mission: Execute canonicalization/migration in practice: run the best available canonicalization script to copy/move deliverables from runtime/outputs/** and agent-specific directories into /outputs/**, then run the artifact index generator to emit /outputs/ARTIFACT_INDEX.md and /outputs/ARTIFACT_INDEX.json that point only to canonical paths. Save the run transcript under /outputs/qa/logs/. Rationale: deliverables are scattered; reviewers/validators cannot reliably discover artifacts.
